{
    "version": 6,
    "bundle": "INEIBUFYAC3WIWN57JSWJPCIAUKHFEB7",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "041110005",
    "title": "1枚の重み、いつか振り返る日のために",
    "enTitle": "",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『未来のウマ娘の礎』を目指すシーザリオとの物語の幕が上がって、\nしばらく経ったある日。自分たちのもとに、撮影依頼が舞い込んだ。",
            "enText": "It had been a few days since the start of Cesario's \nstory, to become 『A guiding light for future Uma \nMusume』. We got a request to do a photo shoot.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 127,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "『注目ウマ娘とトレーナーの学園生活』か",
                    "enText": "『Daily Life of Uma Musume and Trainer』, huh?",
                    "nextBlock": 2
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6901301746195417976,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『注目ウマ娘』とは、自分たちだけではないだろう。選抜レースを\n共に走ったラインクラフト、エアメサイア、デアリングハート――",
            "enText": "It probably focused on 『Popular Uma Musume』, so not \njust us. Probably the girls that ran the Selection \nrace with her, Rhein Kraft, Air Messiah, Daring Heart――",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 124,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 269,
                    "pathId": 7780739212140971179
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 130,
                    "pathId": -8099675299916174439
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 111,
                    "pathId": -1101988578610757786
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2299282869657006698,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "この世代は、話題を集める実力者が揃っている。その中で存在感を\n示すことは、『礎』になるというシーザリオの夢の糧になるだろう。",
            "enText": "This generation was filled with talented girls who \nattracted attention. Appearing in that environment would \nprobably be a good start to becoming a 『Guiding Light』",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 125,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "撮影でもいい結果を残そう！",
                    "enText": "Let's do our best at the photo shoot too!",
                    "nextBlock": 4
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 162,
                    "pathId": 390294788448965621
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 253,
                    "pathId": 412481798030393975
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 356,
                    "pathId": -1301935265797625662
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4658172455624003520,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シーザリオ",
            "enName": "Cesario",
            "jpText": "本日の撮影、よろしくお願いいたします。\nご期待に添えるよう、精一杯努めます。",
            "enText": "Thank you for handling today's photo shoot. \nWe hope we can live up to your expectations.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 245,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 119,
                    "pathId": 6053271499080306267
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 18,
                    "pathId": 2131613778107877158
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 16,
                    "pathId": 3280756107288457711
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 16,
                    "pathId": -6030739946958191756
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6910008252891520767,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "カメラマン",
            "enName": "Photographer",
            "jpText": "もっとラフな感じで大丈夫ですよ。\nトレーナーさんとの学園生活をテーマに撮りたいので！",
            "enText": "It's fine if you keep things more informal. The theme \nis school-life together with your trainer, after all!",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 206,
            "voiceIdx": 1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 340,
                    "pathId": -2348427340575537398
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6262494700211800127,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シーザリオ",
            "enName": "Cesario",
            "jpText": "ありがとうございます。……おや。\nトレーナーも来られたようです、が――",
            "enText": "Thank you very much. ……Oh. \nLooks like Trainer has arrived, though――",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 232,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "すみません、お待たせしましたっ！",
                    "enText": "Sorry, I made you wait!",
                    "nextBlock": 7
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -6032295338963612779
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -4617586022476807045
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8909364610957400375,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シーザリオ",
            "enName": "Cesario",
            "jpText": "あの……トレーナー、その格好はどうされたのですか？\n普段にも増して、随分とかっちりしてらっしゃいますね。",
            "enText": "Um……Trainer, what's with those clothes? \nYou're dressed much more smartly than normal.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 278,
            "voiceIdx": 3,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "大事な撮影だから、頑張ろうと思って！",
                    "enText": "This is important so I wanted to do my best!",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 129,
                    "pathId": 1199585709560311719
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 130,
                    "pathId": -7292155901051042356
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3507390931799489009,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "少しでも写真写りをよくしようと、スーツを新調し、\n美容院でヘアセットも済ませてきた。準備は完璧だ。",
            "enText": "To look better in the photos, I bought a new suit and \nhad my hair done at a salon. My preparations were perfect!",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 108,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 129,
                    "pathId": -3683399713696731916
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 170,
                    "pathId": -3534228185500045648
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4962345530423959532,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シーザリオ",
            "enName": "Cesario",
            "jpText": "なるほど。それは心強いですね。\nではトレーナーも、今日はよろしくお願いします。",
            "enText": "I see. That's reassuring. \nThen Trainer too, I'm looking forward to working with you.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 256,
            "voiceIdx": 4,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -422632042425630218
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 6962275610473498341
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7488533286645621931,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "カメラマン",
            "enName": "Photographer",
            "jpText": "まずは、打ち合わせ中の写真を何枚か！\nいつものお2人といったイメージでお願いします！",
            "enText": "Then to start with, some photos when meeting up! \nPlease think about the image of your normal day!",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 246,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 337,
                    "pathId": 7713358639767850539
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -771197066611193884,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シーザリオ",
            "enName": "Cesario",
            "jpText": "わかりました。では――",
            "enText": "Understood. Then――",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 75,
            "voiceIdx": 6,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": -6816945835113244363
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": 5613461728026053072
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3046365066829806607,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シーザリオ",
            "enName": "Cesario",
            "jpText": "トレーナー、次のレースについて相談しておきたいことが。",
            "enText": "Trainer, I'd like to consult with you about the next race.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 132,
            "voiceIdx": 7,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "いいぞ！とことん話そう、さあさあっ！",
                    "enText": "Sounds good! Let's get to it!",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "いいよ！とことん話そう、さあさあっ！",
                    "enText": "Sounds good! Let's get to it!",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 190,
                    "pathId": 1177425073606833260
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8584804644509272218,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "カメラマン",
            "enName": "Photographer",
            "jpText": "ト、トレーナーさんは少し張り切りすぎな気もしますが……\n打ち合わせ中ですしね。はい、真剣さはしっかり伝わってきますよ！",
            "enText": "T-Trainer-san, I know you're a little fired up but \n……remember, it's supposed to be a meeting. Yeah, \nlet's try to convey a serious atmosphere!",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 381,
            "voiceIdx": 8,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 253,
                    "pathId": -140248796310502434
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 23,
                    "pathId": -7987383925858050085
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7223431213395546153,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シーザリオ",
            "enName": "Cesario",
            "jpText": "次は、休み時間の談笑中の1コマですか。\nなら――",
            "enText": "Next is, chatting while on break. \nThen――",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 205,
            "voiceIdx": 9,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 246,
                    "pathId": -7662200180562979855
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7832847966422723011,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シーザリオ",
            "enName": "Cesario",
            "jpText": "トレーナー。今日は多めにおかずを作ったのですが、\nよろしければ一緒に昼食をとりませんか？",
            "enText": "Trainer. I made a lot of side dishes today, \nif you'd like, how about joining me for lunch?",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 238,
            "voiceIdx": 10,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 334,
                    "pathId": 4250896060922531416
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6058722602761824861,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "カメラマン",
            "enName": "Photographer",
            "jpText": "いいですね～！　凜とした佇まいの中にも、和やかさが見えます！\nトレーナーさんは――",
            "enText": "That's good～! Even with that dignified appearance, \nit's still a cozy atmosphere! Trainer-san――",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 286,
            "voiceIdx": 11,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "やった～！！お誘いありがとう！！",
                    "enText": "Yeah～!! Thanks for asking!!",
                    "nextBlock": 17
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 334,
                    "pathId": -6231030556212090930
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7488697791912856573,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シーザリオ",
            "enName": "Cesario",
            "jpText": "……あの、トレーナー。少し大袈裟といいますか……。\n普段通りの笑顔が、1番素敵に写ると思うのですが……。",
            "enText": "……Um, Trainer. I think you might be over acting…… \nYour normal smile would make the best photo……",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 335,
            "voiceIdx": 12,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "えっ！？もしかしてやりすぎ……！？",
                    "enText": "Eh? Am I trying too hard……!?",
                    "nextBlock": 18
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 303,
                    "pathId": 3645232079389036954
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2053877965122101220,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "カメラマン",
            "enName": "Photographer",
            "jpText": "え、ええと……あの、よかったら少し休憩を挟みましょうか！\n慣れていないと撮影って疲れるものですからね。",
            "enText": "W-weeell……Um, how about taking a short break!? If you're not \nused to it, a photoshoot can be really tiring, after all.",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 361,
            "voiceIdx": 13,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 404,
                    "pathId": -5376093357701632850
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 312,
                    "pathId": -2657582462759520096
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7016697982570275764,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "シーザリオのためにと思って臨んだのだが、その意気込みが\n裏目に出てしまった。これではまるで空気の読めない道化だ。",
            "enText": "I thought I was doing this for Cesario, but it \nseems like my enthusiasm backfired. I was just \nacting like an idiot who couldn't read the mood.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 118,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ごめん、足引っ張ってるな……",
                    "enText": "Sorry, I'm holding you back……",
                    "nextBlock": 20
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "ごめん、足引っ張ってるね……",
                    "enText": "Sorry, I'm holding you back……",
                    "nextBlock": 20
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 196,
                    "pathId": 4714179755987025237
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 13,
                    "pathId": 8182542723182084693
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7094205460760907749,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シーザリオ",
            "enName": "Cesario",
            "jpText": "いえ、そんなことは。気になさらないでください。\nそれよりも大丈夫ですか？　かなり力んでいるように見えますが。",
            "enText": "No, that's not true. Please don't worry about it. But, are you okay? \nIt seems like you're putting quite a lot of effort in to it.",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 329,
            "voiceIdx": 14,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "だって未来の教え子にも見られる写真だし！",
                    "enText": "But your future students will see the photo!",
                    "nextBlock": 21
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 161,
                    "pathId": 2562382555304772706
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -7008412423039240809
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8061035879162606608,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シーザリオ",
            "enName": "Cesario",
            "jpText": "……？　それは、どういう……。",
            "enText": "……? What do you mean……?",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 133,
            "voiceIdx": 15,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -5811912664621685665
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8208785187696166347,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "彼女がレースで活躍を重ねて歴史に残り、『礎』となったのち、\n今日の写真も未来で振り返られるはず――その考えを彼女に伝えた。",
            "enText": "With her success in racing her name will remain in history, \nonce she becomes the 『Guiding Light』, people will look \nback and see these photos――that's what I tell her.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 124,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "だからこそ、1枚も気を抜けなくて……！",
                    "enText": "That's why I need to keep it together……!",
                    "nextBlock": 23
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 200,
                    "pathId": 7808398981355973744
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3280789804901890276,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シーザリオ",
            "enName": "Cesario",
            "jpText": "今日の撮影をそんなふうに……。\nだからスーツも新調したと。",
            "enText": "So that's what you were thinking about today's \nphotoshoot……and why you bought a new suit.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 185,
            "voiceIdx": 16,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 200,
                    "pathId": 7384221775323196321
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 130,
                    "pathId": 6644160376907020830
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4777686398604365977,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シーザリオ",
            "enName": "Cesario",
            "jpText": "……その未来には、いつ辿り着けるのかわからないというのに。\nすでに見据え、そのように備えているだなんて――",
            "enText": "……Even though we don't know when we'll even reach that point. \nTo think you're already looking ahead and preparing for it――",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 349,
            "voiceIdx": 17,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 383,
                    "pathId": 6689212090298799485
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": -5151663227046331081
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8528586900074048881,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シーザリオ",
            "enName": "Cesario",
            "jpText": "やはり貴方が『パートナー』でよかった。\n……ありがとうございます。この言葉以外に、今は何も。",
            "enText": "Really, I'm glad you're my 『Partner』 ……Thank you very much. \nI can't think of any better words to describe how I feel now.",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 314,
            "voiceIdx": 18,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "シーザリオ……",
                    "enText": "Cesario……",
                    "nextBlock": 26
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 323,
                    "pathId": 6054212608320234980
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": -2980250873337237586
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2384946143964502263,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "（カシャ！）",
            "enText": "(Click!)",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 32,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 43,
                    "pathId": -2178293853385729957
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3585045949708671898,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "カメラマン",
            "enName": "Photographer",
            "jpText": "あっ、休憩中なのにすみません！\n2人ともあまりにいい表情だったので、つい！",
            "enText": "Ah, I'm sorry, even though you're on break! You both had \nsuch good expressions on your faces that I couldn't help it!",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 241,
            "voiceIdx": 19,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 158,
                    "pathId": 5213208951420035106
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 279,
                    "pathId": 3809198003898413734
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5268590970630881819,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "カメラマン",
            "enName": "Photographer",
            "jpText": "ですが今日のベストショットをいただきました！\n言葉ではなく目で通じ合う、さすがは注目のコンビです！",
            "enText": "But, because of that, I got the best shot of the day! Not with words, \nbut with the look in your eyes, as expected of a noteworthy duo!",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 293,
            "voiceIdx": 20,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 357,
                    "pathId": -9024315722010180677
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 359,
                    "pathId": 8059221070528860581
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 307359016322307691,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シーザリオ",
            "enName": "Cesario",
            "jpText": "トレーナー、期待に応えられてよかったですね。\nありのままの私たちを残せたようですし。",
            "enText": "Trainer, I'm glad we could live up to expectations. Looks like \nwe were able to leave behind a memory of how we normally are.",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 238,
            "voiceIdx": 21,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": -2503595197005665058
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 24,
                    "pathId": 871554138061564211
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4549730485635965109,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シーザリオ",
            "enName": "Cesario",
            "jpText": "ではこの後も、どんなシチュエーションでも普段通りに。\nそんな私たちを、多く撮影していただきましょう。",
            "enText": "Then, from now on, let's try to meet every situation as our \nnormal selves. So there can be many pictures of us like that.",
